import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import Fondo from '../../assets/img/microsoft-teams-logo-0.png';
import Sharepoint from '../../assets/img'
import { CardGroup } from 'react-bootstrap';

export const BasicExample = () => {
  return (
    <CardGroup className='cardTeams'> 
        <Card className='cardTeams'>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={Fondo}/>
        <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>Microsoft Teams</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>
            Realiza llamadas al instante con Microsoft Teams.
            </Card.Text>
            <Button variant="primary">Conectar a videollamada</Button>
        </Card.Body>
        </Card>

        <Card className='cardTeams'>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={Fondo}/>
        <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>SharePoint</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>
            Realiza llamadas al instante con Microsoft Teams.
            </Card.Text>
            <Button variant="primary">Subir Archivos</Button>
        </Card.Body>
        </Card>

    </CardGroup>
  );
}
